{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/line-bot-by-claude/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"新竹阿平開發筆記 - Hsin Chu RP's Dev Note"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f9a7a734-cb08-5596-b475-5238a4cb1f1c","excerpt":"如何與 Claude 互動來撰寫 LineBot! 在這篇教學文章中，我們將介紹如何與 Claude 互動以撰寫一個符合特定需求的 LineBot。這個 LineBot 需要每天推送 CNN 和 NHK…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/rp-blogger/static/e9f6bccfa4d426e356d6d9a24cc82abb/2bef9/index-image.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"index-image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/rp-blogger/static/e9f6bccfa4d426e356d6d9a24cc82abb/f058b/index-image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/rp-blogger/static/e9f6bccfa4d426e356d6d9a24cc82abb/c26ae/index-image.png 158w,\n/rp-blogger/static/e9f6bccfa4d426e356d6d9a24cc82abb/6bdcf/index-image.png 315w,\n/rp-blogger/static/e9f6bccfa4d426e356d6d9a24cc82abb/f058b/index-image.png 630w,\n/rp-blogger/static/e9f6bccfa4d426e356d6d9a24cc82abb/40601/index-image.png 945w,\n/rp-blogger/static/e9f6bccfa4d426e356d6d9a24cc82abb/2bef9/index-image.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>如何與 Claude 互動來撰寫 LineBot!</h3>\n<p>在這篇教學文章中，我們將介紹如何與 Claude 互動以撰寫一個符合特定需求的 LineBot。這個 LineBot 需要每天推送 CNN 和 NHK 的新聞標題以及台灣股票價格，並能根據用戶訊息回覆相應內容。整個過程將逐步展示如何分解需求並撰寫對應的程式碼。</p>\n<h3>開工前的準備</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>準備好 LineBot 帳號</li>\n<li>準備好 Claude 3 帳號</li>\n<li>準備好 Gemini API Key (免費的太香了)</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>步驟一：明確需求</h3>\n<p>首先，讓我們清楚列出我們的需求:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>我希望我的chatbot可以推送新聞給我，還可以定時告訴我股價訊息（小弟的公司不能用私人手機 QQ）。</li>\n<li>可以隨時當我的AI小助手，</li>\n</ol>\n<p>稍微整理一下需求後，我們可以接著把實作的一些細節展開：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>與 Line 整合的聊天機器人</li>\n<li>每天 UTC +8 時間 8:30 推送 CNN 和 NHK 的新聞標題，包含超連結</li>\n<li>每天 UTC +8 時間 12:00 推送台灣股票價格（股票代號：00929, 0056, 006208）</li>\n<li>當用戶發送文字訊息時，機器人應將訊息傳送給 Gemini API 並返回結果</li>\n<li>所有的密鑰、API 金鑰和 tokens 都應該從環境變數中讀取</li>\n<li>使用 Flask 和 Unicorn 運行聊天機器人</li>\n<li>當用戶訊息為 \"news\" 時，顯示新聞標題</li>\n<li>當用戶訊息為 \"stocks\" 時，顯示股票價格</li>\n<li>使用 Flask blueprint 來組織程式碼</li>\n<li>最後，寫一個 Dockerfile 來容器化這個聊天機器人</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>步驟二：與 Claude 碰撞出答案</h3>\n<p>整理完之後就可以來壓榨 Claude 拉，我這邊會使用 Claude 3.5 Sonnet 來處理我的需求\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/rp-blogger/static/b111797c18a4905593ff725572d6bc40/7575b/prompt-01.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.48101265822784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"prompt-01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/rp-blogger/static/b111797c18a4905593ff725572d6bc40/f058b/prompt-01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/rp-blogger/static/b111797c18a4905593ff725572d6bc40/c26ae/prompt-01.png 158w,\n/rp-blogger/static/b111797c18a4905593ff725572d6bc40/6bdcf/prompt-01.png 315w,\n/rp-blogger/static/b111797c18a4905593ff725572d6bc40/f058b/prompt-01.png 630w,\n/rp-blogger/static/b111797c18a4905593ff725572d6bc40/40601/prompt-01.png 945w,\n/rp-blogger/static/b111797c18a4905593ff725572d6bc40/78612/prompt-01.png 1260w,\n/rp-blogger/static/b111797c18a4905593ff725572d6bc40/7575b/prompt-01.png 1608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>輸入後 Claude 就會刷刷刷的把答案寫出來了，所有產生的 Code 可以在右側去點開來看:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.53164556962025%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"prompt-02\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/rp-blogger/static/1fd1e243c32158872ba2939f7a8a67de/f058b/prompt-02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/rp-blogger/static/1fd1e243c32158872ba2939f7a8a67de/c26ae/prompt-02.png 158w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1fd1e243c32158872ba2939f7a8a67de/6bdcf/prompt-02.png 315w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1fd1e243c32158872ba2939f7a8a67de/f058b/prompt-02.png 630w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1fd1e243c32158872ba2939f7a8a67de/40601/prompt-02.png 945w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1fd1e243c32158872ba2939f7a8a67de/78612/prompt-02.png 1260w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1fd1e243c32158872ba2939f7a8a67de/e80ec/prompt-02.png 2582w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n這裡我修正 Claude 對於 flask blueprint 的誤解，Claude 馬上做出修正:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"prompt-03\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/rp-blogger/static/d129cbf9007f1886fb30b91176d2efbb/f058b/prompt-03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/rp-blogger/static/d129cbf9007f1886fb30b91176d2efbb/c26ae/prompt-03.png 158w,\n/rp-blogger/static/d129cbf9007f1886fb30b91176d2efbb/6bdcf/prompt-03.png 315w,\n/rp-blogger/static/d129cbf9007f1886fb30b91176d2efbb/f058b/prompt-03.png 630w,\n/rp-blogger/static/d129cbf9007f1886fb30b91176d2efbb/40601/prompt-03.png 945w,\n/rp-blogger/static/d129cbf9007f1886fb30b91176d2efbb/78612/prompt-03.png 1260w,\n/rp-blogger/static/d129cbf9007f1886fb30b91176d2efbb/70d4c/prompt-03.png 2548w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n可以看到 Claude 雖然根據 blueprint 把 API 分開了，但是並沒有實作 function 內容，因為 Claude 以為我們的 blueprint 是指 function 要留空。\n這裡我們可以再修正他一次:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.37974683544304%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt text\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/rp-blogger/static/1c9095cf41edf551aa44aa5027336901/f058b/image-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/rp-blogger/static/1c9095cf41edf551aa44aa5027336901/c26ae/image-1.png 158w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1c9095cf41edf551aa44aa5027336901/6bdcf/image-1.png 315w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1c9095cf41edf551aa44aa5027336901/f058b/image-1.png 630w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1c9095cf41edf551aa44aa5027336901/40601/image-1.png 945w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1c9095cf41edf551aa44aa5027336901/78612/image-1.png 1260w,\n/rp-blogger/static/1c9095cf41edf551aa44aa5027336901/2a333/image-1.png 1484w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n這裡 Claude 又開始刷刷刷的寫起程式。完成後我們看一下，發現 Claude 選用了兩個 <a href=\"https://newsapi.org\">newsapi</a> 跟 <a href=\"https://www.alphavantage.co\">alphavantage</a> 來取得新聞跟股票資訊。稍微看一下會發現這兩個 API 有點殺雞用牛刀，於是我要求 Claude 用 yfinance 與 RSS parser 來實作:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.810126582278485%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt text\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/rp-blogger/static/fc37af7b022b605fbf3f8703abd603be/f058b/image-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/rp-blogger/static/fc37af7b022b605fbf3f8703abd603be/c26ae/image-2.png 158w,\n/rp-blogger/static/fc37af7b022b605fbf3f8703abd603be/6bdcf/image-2.png 315w,\n/rp-blogger/static/fc37af7b022b605fbf3f8703abd603be/f058b/image-2.png 630w,\n/rp-blogger/static/fc37af7b022b605fbf3f8703abd603be/40601/image-2.png 945w,\n/rp-blogger/static/fc37af7b022b605fbf3f8703abd603be/0d0e4/image-2.png 1230w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.645569620253163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt text\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/rp-blogger/static/082aff2295ef63a272c3fbec469d40f7/f058b/image-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/rp-blogger/static/082aff2295ef63a272c3fbec469d40f7/c26ae/image-3.png 158w,\n/rp-blogger/static/082aff2295ef63a272c3fbec469d40f7/6bdcf/image-3.png 315w,\n/rp-blogger/static/082aff2295ef63a272c3fbec469d40f7/f058b/image-3.png 630w,\n/rp-blogger/static/082aff2295ef63a272c3fbec469d40f7/40601/image-3.png 945w,\n/rp-blogger/static/082aff2295ef63a272c3fbec469d40f7/c1b63/image-3.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n最後，一套全靠嘴砲的 LineBot 就出生了。由於前面有要求所有 Secrets 都必須用環境變數取得，只需要在部署時提供變數就能跑起來啦</p>\n<p>這次分享的 source code 在<a href=\"https://github.com/tig4605246/Claude-LineBot-Example\">這裡</a>\n只要把指令描述清楚，就能讓 Claude 正確地幫你當碼農。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"建立 Line AI 聊天機器人全靠嘴砲！","date":"August 03, 2024","description":"用嘴巴讓 Claude 3.5 寫出bot，再部署到喜歡的地方"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/special-thanks/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Special Thanks"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"f9a7a734-cb08-5596-b475-5238a4cb1f1c","previousPostId":"2478ac7a-d119-575f-8a12-03781c278ba5","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"],"slicesMap":{}}